  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">WR- Words: The Silent W Pattern</h2>

<p>The WR- prefix is the most productive W+consonant combination. The W is silent in speech but scores a full 4 points on the board. These words are common and rarely challenged.</p>

